    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā … pe … ",
          "en": "Then a brahmin cosmologist went up to the Buddha … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:1.3",
          "pli": "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Seated to one side he said to the Buddha: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:2.1",
          "pli": "“Kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamatthī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Master Gotama, does all exist?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:2.2",
          "pli": "“‘Sabbamatthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, jeṭṭhametaṃ lokāyataṃ”. ",
          "en": "“‘All exists’: this is the oldest cosmology, brahmin.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:3.1",
          "pli": "“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṃ natthī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Then does all not exist?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:3.2",
          "pli": "“‘Sabbaṃ natthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, dutiyametaṃ lokāyataṃ”. ",
          "en": "“‘All doesn’t exist’: this is the second cosmology. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:4.1",
          "pli": "“Kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamekattan”ti? ",
          "en": "“Well, is all a unity?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:4.2",
          "pli": "“‘Sabbamekattan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, tatiyametaṃ lokāyataṃ”. ",
          "en": "“‘All is a unity’: this is the third cosmology. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:5.1",
          "pli": "“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṃ puthuttan”ti? ",
          "en": "“Then is all a plurality?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:5.2",
          "pli": "“‘Sabbaṃ puthuttan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, catutthametaṃ lokāyataṃ. ",
          "en": "“‘All is a plurality’: this is the fourth cosmology. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.1",
          "pli": "Ete te, brāhmaṇa, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathāgato dhammaṃ deseti: ",
          "en": "Avoiding these two extremes, the Realized One teaches by the middle way: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.2",
          "pli": "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā; ",
          "en": "‘Ignorance is a condition for choices. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.3",
          "pli": "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": "Choices are a condition for consciousness. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.4",
          "pli": "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ",
          "en": "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.5",
          "pli": "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho; ",
          "en": "When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.6",
          "pli": "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe … ",
          "en": "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:6.7",
          "pli": "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti. ",
          "en": "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:7.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ vutte, lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "When he said this, the brahmin cosmologist said to the Buddha, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:7.2",
          "pli": "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … ",
          "en": "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:7.3",
          "pli": "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. ",
          "en": "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn12.48:7.4",
          "pli": "Aṭṭhamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
